---
title: Pulled Buffalo Chicken Bowl with Quinoa, Corn, Avocado and Feta
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour, this dish gives you the fiesta without the fuss! Quinoa, corn and avocado pair perfectly with tender chicken for a fun bowl that comes together with our fabulous hot sauce.
